{
  "stem": "766.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I answered her again, in German, my crime is that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because there was no other reason to call me crime.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So at that moment, she wasn't too bad to say.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But she could take out the-- the-- the whatever and give me right away, or send me back to Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "How do I dare to open the mouth?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And she was wearing a uniform with a swastika, with everything.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But I told her that my crime is that I am Jewish.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Guben?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Guben is near Breslau?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Near Breslau.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the-- I-- if I remember well, the girls were working in the factory of electrical wires, supplies.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this was a [?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Lawrence ?] factory.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, about 100, more maybe.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I couldn't tell you.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So when I settled-- she-- so she-- everything fine for me, the doctor.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "In the [NON-ENGLISH], like, the hospital, was a room for me, and water, and hot water for the hospital and me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was-- I was surprised.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she tells me, now comes a crucial moment so in my life.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She told me I should sit down and write orders, what she-- supply, what I need to--",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "To run the hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "--to run the hospital.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So I sat down.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't remember a thing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I didn't remember my name, by the way.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Because the shock from the few days in Auschwitz, what they-- I didn't remember.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But-- so maybe she didn't insist.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But now she left, and left me in the room with paper and a pencil, I should write the supply.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I don't remember one word.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I said, because now she will think I'm not a doctor.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now she will think I am crazy.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Because I remember the others over there, crazy.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
